data.title: HM Norodom Sihanouk King of Cambodia
data.meta_description:
The life and times of His Majesty 
Norodom Sihanouk, King of Cambodia, as seen through the 28 films which 
he produced, directed, and scored music.
data.text:
This site is dedicated to a very talented man who happens to be King.

Please watch this space as it evolves into the life and times of HM Norodom Sihanouk concentrating on the movies he has directed, produced and scored the music.

Norodom Sihanouk, the King of Cambodia, is also a film producer, movie director, amd musician. He has made many movies, written musical pieces, and muscial scores for his movies. In this web site, the life and times of His Majesty Norodom Sihanouk, King of Cambodia, is seen through his films and his music.
